Eclipso's Deadly Doubles!!: Bruce Gordon and Professer Bennet try to trap Eclipso in another dimension to rid the world of his evil.
The Return of the Morloo: Doctor-7 escapes from jail and immediately conjures up the deadly Morloo again, so Mark Merlin calls on a Morloo of his own from the same dimension to even the odds.
